目录设计：

web层           com.book.web/servlet/controller

service层       com.book.service            service接口包
                com.book.service.impl       service接口实现包

dao持久层       com.book.dao                dao接口包
                com.book.dao.impl           dao接口实现类

实体bean对象    com.book.pojo/entity/domain/bean   javaBean类

测试包          com.book.test/junit        测试类

工具类          com.book.utils             工具类包